original_title: Die Herrin der Welt 2. Teil - Die Geschichte der Maud Gregaards
overview: Maud Gregaards tells her rescuer, the Chinese Dr. Kien-Lung, her life: Her father was an archivist in the Foreign Office who was run by the unscrupulous Dr. Frohner was blackmailed into giving him a secret Chinese treaty.
title: The Mistress of the World, Part II: The Race for Life
